      "text": "I see.\n\nI'm debating if \"Update-\" is the right verb for this scenario / module.\n\nThe module can also manipulate packages, so it feels like Update- might fit better for \"make changes to a package\"\n\ni.e. Update-*** -Replace foo, bar \n\nClear- seems like it could work\n\nClear-*** -OldVersion"
